docs.abstract: The consumer products giant has had a base in both London and Rotterdam for decades, but it is moving to simplify its corporate structure.

docs.lead_paragraph: LONDON — Unilever said on Thursday that it would make Rotterdam, the Netherlands, its sole headquarters, dealing a symbolic blow to Britain as it negotiates its exit from the European Union.
